name: At Home 2012 Tax Return
summary: Learn about .T12 files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: Completed tax returns can be printed and mailed or filed directly from within the software. At Home is available in Basic, Deluxe, Premium, and Premium & Business editions.
NOTE: At Home 2012 can also import data from At Home 2011 (.T11) files.

description: Tax return created with the 2012 version of H&R Block At Home tax preparation software; includes United States federal tax forms for the 2012 tax year; may also contain state tax forms if a state return has been selected; stores data entered by the user so the tax return can be saved and continued at a later time.
